comments.body: These tests are good. Consider declaring the proto string inside the function function itself, so that one can read everything there is to know about the test without scrolling back and forth.
This sounds good to me, I put the proto strings inside each test in `b00c93e`.
Be careful about making these checks too exhaustive. We don't want modifications to the code to require updating this test too often.
